🤖 **Common input mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| No validation | Add validation logic |
| No loading state | Show progress indicator |
| Wrong keyboard | Use `KeyboardOptions` |
| No error display | Show error messages |
| No clear button | Add clear functionality |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Add validation
if (text.length < 3) {
    Text("Minimum 3 characters", color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.error)
}

// 2. Show loading
if (isLoading) {
    CircularProgressIndicator()
} else {
    Text("Submit")
}

// 3. Correct keyboard
KeyboardOptions(keyboardType = KeyboardType.Number)

// 4. Show errors
if (error != null) {
    Text(error, color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.error)
}

// 5. Add clear button
Button(onClick = { text = "" }) { Text("Clear") }
